Package: gitlab
Architecture: all
Pre-Depends: adduser
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, bundler, curl, dialog, git, libicu44, libmagic1,
 libpython2.7 | libpython2.6, postfix | mail-transport-agent, mysql-server | postgresql,
 python-docutils, python-pygments, redis-server (>= 2:2.4.0), ruby (>= 1.9.3), sudo
Description: Self hosted Git management software
 GitLab allows you to
 * keep your code secure on your own server
 * manage repositories, users and access permissions
 * communicate though issues, line-comments and wiki's
 * perform code reviews with merge requests
 .
 GitLab is
 * powered by Ruby on Rails
 * completely free and open source (MIT license)
 * used by 10.000 organization to keep their code secure
